        "description": "<p>YARPP for bbpress is a simple plugin that enables your bbpress content to be included in YARPP results.</p>\n<p>Once you install this plugin, simply go to Settings &gt;&gt; Related Posts (YARPP) and forums, topics and<br />\nreplies will automatically be included in your &#8220;Pool&#8221;.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<p>Simple install and you&#8217;re ready to go!</p>\n<p>Note:</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking to include bbpress results as related posts to other post types (pages, posts, etc),<br />\nyou will need to check the box &#8220;Display results from all post types&#8221; located under &#8220;Relatedness&#8221; options.</p>\n",
        "faq": "\n<h4>Is it really that easy?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Why hasn&#8217;t anyone built this before?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Beats me.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Can I buy you a beer?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Sure!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&amp;hosted_button_id=RDLSNVQESKF6W\" title=\"Buy me a beer\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Donate</a></p>\n</p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Built it and it&#8217;s perfect.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
